---
description: Secret handling, MCP permissions, external services and production safety
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- Never request secrets in normal chat.
- Prefer browser OAuth and official CLI login.
- Keep development secrets in untracked `.env.local`; deployment secrets in provider stores.
- Start MCP access read-only and project-scoped where supported.
- Explain and request approval before installing any MCP.
- Never connect production, real patients or live WhatsApp during development.
- Ask before administrator commands, purchases, destructive actions or production changes.
